quran[29{c,v,t}:
37,154,"tumhe kya ho gaya hai, kaisay hukum laga rahay ho"
37,155,kya tumhe hosh nahi aata
37,156,ya phir tumahray paas apni un baton ke liye koi saaf sanad hai
37,157,to lao apni woh kitaab agar tum sachey ho
37,158,"unhon ne Allah aur mulaika ke darmain nasb ka rishta bana rakha hai, halaank mulaika khoob jantay hain ke yeh log mujrim ki hesiyat se paish honay walay hain"
37,159,"( aur woh kehte hain ke )"" Allah unn sifaat se pak hai"
37,160,jo uss ke khalis bundon ke siwa dosray log is ki taraf mansoob karte hain
37,161,pas tum aur tumahray yeh mabood
37,162,Allah se kisi ko phair nahi satke
37,163,magar sirf uss ko jo dozakh ki bharakti hui aag mein jhlsne wala ho
37,164,aur hamara haal to yeh hai ke hum mein se har aik ka aik maqam muqarrar hai
37,165,aur hum saf basta khidmat gaar hain
37,166,"aur tasbeeh karne walay hain """
37,167,yeh log pehlay to kaha karte thay
37,168,"ke kash hamaray paas woh"" zikar"" hota jo pichli qomon ko mila tha"
37,169,to hum Allah ke cheeda bande hotay
37,170,magar ( jab woh aa gaya ) to unhon ne is ka inkaar kar diya ab anqareeb aِnhin ( iss rawish ka nateeja ) maloom ho jaye ga
37,171,apne beje hue bundon se hum pehlay hi wada kar chuke hain
37,172,ke yaqeenan un ki madad ki jaye gi
37,173,aur hamara lashkar hi ghalib ho kar rahay ga
37,174,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, zara kuch mddt taq inhen inn ke haal par chore do"
37,175,"aur dekhte raho, anqareeb yeh khud bhi dekh len ge"
37,176,kya yeh hamaray azaab ke liye jaldi macha rahay hain ?
37,177,jab woh inn ke sehan mein aa utre ga to woh din unn logon ke liye bohat bura ho ga jinhein mutnabba kya ja chuka hai
37,178,bas zara aِnhin kuch muddat ke liye chore do
37,179,"aur dekhte raho, anqareeb yeh khud dekh len ge"
37,180,"pak hai tera rab, izzat ka maalik, unn tamam baton se jo yeh log bana rahay hain"
37,181,aur salam hai mursaleen par
37,182,aur saari tareef Allah Rab alaalmin hi ke liye hai
